Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.69,0:00:33.96,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,266)}以一顆頑固的心
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.96,0:00:37.35,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,266)}石塊可以去往任何地方
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.35,0:00:40.71,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,266)}如同砂土般輕易崩壞
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.71,0:00:44.03,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,266)}無法預知一字的未來
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.03,0:00:46.29,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,266)}don't believe in action
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.29,0:00:50.51,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,266)}如若只是一味向前則會迷失所有
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.51,0:00:52.86,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,266)}show me your emotion
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.86,0:01:00.24,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,666)}請賜予我無法用語言形容的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.50,0:01:03.81,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,266)}一顆冰冷的石頭
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.81,0:01:07.15,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,266)}恐怕也隱藏著炙熱的溫度吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.15,0:01:10.51,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,266)}既然已經決定 那就想要取得勝利
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.51,0:01:13.89,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,266)}空無一物的未來
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.89,0:01:16.10,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,266)}you are my illusion
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.10,0:01:20.43,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,266)}就算只有一顆空洞的心也沒有關係
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.43,0:01:22.72,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,666)}show me your addiction
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.72,0:01:26.51,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,266)}追尋緊閉的夢境
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.51,0:01:30.30,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,266)}把一切交給氣勢 握緊的雙手
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.30,0:01:33.56,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,266)}絕對能夠改變你的人生signal
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.56,0:01:36.33,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,266)}如此思念你 哪怕就算飛翔
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.33,0:01:40.19,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(120,266)}也終會墜落消失
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.19,0:01:43.51,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,266)}再一次衝上天空
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.51,0:01:46.83,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,266)}抱緊所有拋下的思念
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.83,0:01:49.67,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,266)}就算哭泣 也一起承擔
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.67,0:01:52.69,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,266)}直到你微笑的那一天
