Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.25,0:00:09.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼啊 週六啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.95,0:00:12.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍微再睡一會…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.91,0:00:19.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學園祭的準備
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.23,0:00:22.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 不好 遲到了

Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.97,0:02:03.97,OT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(600,500)}學院祭的鬼

Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.77,0:00:28.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好…痛!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.18,0:02:21.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學園祭
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.31,0:02:26.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我成為新理事長以來的首次重要活動
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.72,0:02:30.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還剩下一天
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.16,0:02:32.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無論如何也要撐過去
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.04,0:02:41.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總覺得心跳不已騷動不已啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.03,0:02:44.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喔 萌啊萌啊鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.57,0:02:46.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個漢字錯了 鬼瓦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.73,0:02:48.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是火焰的燃
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.11,0:02:50.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說回來
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.82,0:02:54.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將軍屋的「MOERO OORE」真是效果出眾啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.18,0:02:58.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能讓大小姐如此幹勁十足
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.06,0:03:00.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幹勁十足…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.94,0:03:02.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個氣氛的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.51,0:03:04.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.69,0:03:08.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好近 太近了 鏡同學
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.79,0:03:12.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且還想順勢就去握住人家的手
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.40,0:03:14.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳們在搞什麼呢 太失禮了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.64,0:03:18.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然突然就跑進來拍照 真不敢相信
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.29,0:03:20.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我拜託她們的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.68,0:03:27.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我拜託她們「留下學院祭記錄的」 對吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.94,0:03:31.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 再稍微往左邊一點點
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.03,0:03:33.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對對
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.14,0:03:34.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 OK
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.27,0:03:36.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼新理事長的瑠璃醬
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.39,0:03:38.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請對明天的學園祭發表一下看法吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.10,0:03:39.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.71,0:03:43.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是理事長藍羽瑠璃
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.73,0:03:46.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上任以來的首次學園祭
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.23,0:03:48.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我衷心希望能夠與大家一起盡興
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.24,0:03:50.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成功辦好這個活動
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.58,0:03:54.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣～可不行～蛋蛋啊鬼…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.74,0:03:57.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行喔啊鬼…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.76,0:04:03.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我平時跟你說過多少次了 別在普通人的面前說話
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.67,0:04:05.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,緊急情況啊鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.43,0:04:08.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,附近有惡石啊鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.85,0:04:09.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在學園裡?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.06,0:04:11.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes啊鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.99,0:04:19.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我膩了 好想回家
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.09,0:04:22.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說 要是這樣都拿不到學分的話
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.22,0:04:24.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們的成績就危險了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.12,0:04:25.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別把我跟你混為一談
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.05,0:04:27.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是一樣嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.29,0:04:29.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不一樣呢 笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.93,0:04:33.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 那個不是丹童子嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.03,0:04:35.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.23,0:04:37.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 沒勁了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.05,0:04:41.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至少善解人意一點 學園祭的時候就別來了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.41,0:04:44.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,倒不如說真希望他退學
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.59,0:04:47.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.14,0:04:53.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在 我是鏡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.11,0:04:55.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你那邊情況如何
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.04,0:04:58.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才真是失禮了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.21,0:05:00.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了讓鬼瓦不再淘氣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.01,0:05:02.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已經好好教育過它了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.63,0:05:03.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請放心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.85,0:05:05.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.45,0:05:09.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 目標是個什麼樣的傢伙？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.89,0:05:13.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連我都能打倒的弱小傢伙啊鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.04,0:05:27.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的位置在…這裡!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.21,0:05:30.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天就是你們的披露舞臺了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.53,0:05:31.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油喔
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.58,0:05:35.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.57,0:05:38.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事沒事 等下再去修好就行
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.71,0:05:44.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呀 個子高很方便吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.44,0:05:47.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,長得高可不是什麼好事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.52,0:05:49.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今早還撞到門楣了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.08,0:05:51.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.41,0:05:53.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還發生了這種事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.28,0:05:54.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那還真要命啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.95,0:05:57.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經不痛了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.95,0:05:58.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.05,0:06:01.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來準備的很順利呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.19,0:06:02.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑠璃醬
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.29,0:06:04.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝妳借我投影機
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.07,0:06:08.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣一來寶物的影像上映會就萬無一失了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.75,0:06:12.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的太感謝了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.71,0:06:16.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定要讓明天的學園祭成功喔
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.51,0:06:17.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.43,0:06:31.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我稍微出去一下
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.91,0:06:33.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.35,0:06:35.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.68,0:06:36.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.44,0:06:38.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.25,0:06:39.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出什麼事了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.39,0:06:43.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一踢那邊的足球 它就變成石頭了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.26,0:06:44.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,變成石頭…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.31,0:06:45.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是莫名其妙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.07,0:06:50.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來是惡石沒錯呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.14,0:06:51.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我不是說了嘛啊鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.84,0:06:53.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.04,0:06:56.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 丹童子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.46,0:06:59.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍微陪我一下
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.15,0:07:02.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.86,0:07:09.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是知道學園暴露在惡石的危險之下
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.33,0:07:13.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那大小姐一定會終止學園祭
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.49,0:07:15.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果鬼瓦的情報正確的話
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.88,0:07:19.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼就靠我一個人應該也能打倒惡石
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.11,0:07:22.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算再怎麼弱小 但惡石也是惡石啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.59,0:07:23.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有個想法
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.01,0:07:25.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊鬼？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.94,0:07:31.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽好了 絕對不要告訴大小姐惡石的事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.79,0:07:39.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 你要繼續回去社團活動嗎啊鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.23,0:07:41.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正在考慮
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.66,0:07:42.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊鬼？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.94,0:07:46.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,確實感應到的反應很微弱
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.39,0:07:48.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但也有進化的可能性吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.76,0:07:50.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes啊鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.32,0:07:55.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼只要我使用sacred的力量 就能確實打倒它了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.10,0:07:57.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,試著去拜託瑠璃嗎啊鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.94,0:08:01.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就說「我要打倒惡石 所以讓我變身吧啊鬼」
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.74,0:08:03.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來學園祭要終止了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.98,0:08:06.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈哈 真好笑
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.99,0:08:08.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.99,0:08:16.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定要讓明天的學園祭成功喔
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.00,0:08:19.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,演一齣戲吧啊鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.88,0:08:22.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要欺騙她嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.84,0:08:24.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過是演戲而已
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.09,0:08:28.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽好了 要死死盯著她的眼睛說出炙熱的臺詞啊鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.81,0:08:31.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳那如同煆燒中瓦片一般的 熱烈閃爍的眼神
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.87,0:08:35.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,點燃了我的鬥志啊鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.33,0:08:39.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起啊 瑠璃醬
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.35,0:08:41.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳明明是理事長 卻來幫我做這種事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.10,0:08:43.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用在意
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.56,0:08:46.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總覺得做這種事還挺開心的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.31,0:08:51.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,理事長室？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.05,0:08:53.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂 是鏡嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.55,0:08:55.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巡視結束了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.58,0:08:58.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 我是阿爾瑪
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.28,0:09:02.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…阿爾瑪同學？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.03,0:09:04.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎 是阿爾瑪同學啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.86,0:09:06.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.04,0:09:07.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.88,0:09:10.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 是氣球破掉的聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.76,0:09:11.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又來了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.46,0:09:13.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個 有什麼事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.30,0:09:16.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我有話想對妳說
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.22,0:09:19.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能來屋頂一下嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.23,0:09:23.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.09,0:09:25.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胸口騷動不已
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.87,0:09:27.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胸…胸口？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.72,0:09:28.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.25,0:09:32.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 沒事 我馬上去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.60,0:09:34.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼待會見
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.71,0:09:41.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在學院內發現了惡石
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.74,0:09:43.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,進入警戒狀態
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.21,0:09:44.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遵命
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.80,0:09:48.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啟動動態檢測跟熱源探測
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.77,0:09:50.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遵命
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.33,0:09:55.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各感測器 沒有異常
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.02,0:09:57.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開始傳送資料
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.88,0:10:01.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同步熱源解析與動態檢測的反應
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.29,0:10:02.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遵命
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.99,0:10:06.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.98,0:10:09.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,惡石不會有熱源反應啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.28,0:10:13.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有 立即把契約裝甲派來學院
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.92,0:10:15.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是在學生面前出動裝備…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.08,0:10:17.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒問題
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.42,0:10:19.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有專門為了這種時候存在的作戰
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.63,0:10:22.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Operation Mirrorforce吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.91,0:10:25.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Operation Mirrorforce？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.85,0:10:29.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,另外 這個任務不能告訴大小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.21,0:10:32.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.29,0:10:36.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說找我有事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.69,0:10:42.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿爾瑪同學         那個啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.96,0:10:44.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是            我的…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.87,0:10:46.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.54,0:10:51.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想更加熟練的使用sacred的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.51,0:10:53.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想為了妳…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.50,0:10:56.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 不對 是為了大家而使用這份力量
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.41,0:10:59.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是呢 這個想法太棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.70,0:11:02.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在能讓我變身嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.37,0:11:04.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.71,0:11:06.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之能當練習啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.40,0:11:10.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也許還能幫忙解決大家的困擾
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.13,0:11:12.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,更重要的是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.62,0:11:19.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳那熱烈閃爍的眼神…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.17,0:11:22.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然不行
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.77,0:11:24.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才的不算
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.40,0:11:25.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.84,0:11:33.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,練習的話 用備用品就足夠了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.75,0:11:35.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.10,0:11:40.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說 這些備用品得多少錢啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.82,0:11:44.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我記得這個好像是1億4千萬
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.18,0:11:45.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,1億？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.54,0:11:48.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有4千萬呢啊鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.36,0:11:53.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你之記憶聚集我身
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.40,0:12:04.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我之「意志」賜予你身
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.02,0:12:08.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總而言之…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.66,0:12:09.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打擾了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.09,0:12:16.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…那個
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.95,0:12:21.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難不成你是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.08,0:12:25.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丹童子…同學？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.26,0:12:47.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個 難不成你是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.56,0:12:50.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丹童子同學？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.34,0:12:53.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 部長 事情是這樣的…那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.78,0:12:57.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Nice cosplay啊 丹童子同學
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.57,0:13:03.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實我正為社團的宣傳傷腦筋呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.21,0:13:07.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呀 你這身打扮的話 宣傳效果一定很驚人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.32,0:13:08.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳說是吧 瑠璃醬
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.69,0:13:11.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 也許真是如此喔
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.33,0:13:12.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宣傳嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.17,0:13:14.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個給你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.49,0:13:15.41,Notes,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓你著迷的石頭 記錄 石頭的24小時
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.54,0:13:31.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Operation Mirrorforce 開始
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.10,0:13:36.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 要加油囉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.93,0:13:38.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳看起來心情很不錯啊鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.82,0:13:41.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為阿爾瑪同學終於有幹勁了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.36,0:13:47.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恐怕她沒想到背後居然是我在牽線搭橋吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.87,0:13:53.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡 速度怎麼這麼快啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.37,0:13:59.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丹童子 變身了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.54,0:14:03.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接到大小姐的聯絡 說是為了訓練才變身的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.80,0:14:05.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個混蛋…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.48,0:14:17.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 臉頰好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.66,0:14:26.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 給我好好道歉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.91,0:14:29.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 真是十分抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.34,0:14:31.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先失陪了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.49,0:14:33.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.71,0:14:34.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鏡同學
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.56,0:14:48.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦 增加了？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.79,0:14:48.31,Notes,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丹童子？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.46,0:14:49.76,Notes,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他原來是這種角色嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.88,0:14:51.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之先追這邊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.36,0:14:54.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目標變成兩個了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.45,0:14:56.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想應該是惡石分裂了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.07,0:14:58.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真棘手啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.75,0:15:01.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鏡同學 你在做什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.78,0:15:04.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真虧你們能做出這個啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.96,0:15:07.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們…非常抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.53,0:15:10.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我現在正在執行任務 所以無暇顧及妳們
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.78,0:15:13.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能不能請妳們儘快回活動室去呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.86,0:15:15.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我先失陪了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.75,0:15:20.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被這樣露骨拒絕的話 反而讓人更想去看個究竟了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.69,0:15:21.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.06,0:15:30.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再不快點就來不及了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.62,0:15:35.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…丹童子嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.05,0:15:38.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然搞這麼誇張的cosplay
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.74,0:15:39.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去哪了？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.74,0:15:42.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好球
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.00,0:15:45.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也來 我扔
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.19,0:15:53.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救命啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.59,0:16:02.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 差不多就這樣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.99,0:16:10.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發生什麼事情了？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.32,0:16:12.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,製作紀念牌的時候發生了事故
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.63,0:16:17.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能不能想點辦法下來？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.44,0:16:18.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.63,0:16:20.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趕快救救我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.91,0:16:24.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.98,0:16:26.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們是朋友吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.02,0:16:29.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們下來的時候為什麼不幫他一把
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.04,0:16:31.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得想個辦法啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.39,0:16:35.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是又不能在眾目睽睽之下使用Sacred Seven的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.18,0:16:46.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 解決掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.37,0:16:47.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下一隻
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.01,0:16:51.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丹童子那傢伙在搞什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.69,0:16:57.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,撐住 救援馬上就到了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.63,0:16:59.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕對不能放鬆力量啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.07,0:16:59.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬上就來了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.61,0:17:02.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經到極限了 不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.43,0:17:26.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.38,0:17:41.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,諸位同學 別擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.51,0:17:43.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對英雄而言沒有不可能的事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.72,0:17:51.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 你沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.49,0:17:54.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你 丹童子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.85,0:17:58.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的太感謝你了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.33,0:18:01.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能站起來嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.41,0:18:08.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,該怎麼說呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.12,0:18:13.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,覺得比起我們 還是丹童子更善良啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.40,0:18:14.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.48,0:18:15.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也這麼認為
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.52,0:18:53.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嚇我一跳
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.94,0:19:09.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.29,0:19:10.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丹童子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.52,0:19:12.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把惡石扔過來
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.33,0:19:13.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.51,0:19:27.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自爆
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.63,0:19:41.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終於收拾掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.49,0:19:49.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管有什麼困擾
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.72,0:19:52.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們英雄都會乾淨俐落地解決掉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.58,0:19:53.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.56,0:19:57.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 收工
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.37,0:20:00.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼啊 原來是拍電影啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.13,0:20:01.28,Notes,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是拍電影啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.52,0:20:03.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.65,0:20:05.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之後就拜託妳了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.52,0:20:06.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遵命
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.33,0:20:10.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Operation Mirrorforce
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.36,0:20:12.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Mission complete
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.38,0:20:19.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然不向我報告 到底是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.82,0:20:21.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我解釋一下 鏡
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.97,0:20:24.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我認為應該優先排除惡石
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.04,0:20:27.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萬幸沒出什麼大事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.76,0:20:31.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但你沒想過會波及到學生們嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.35,0:20:32.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這傢伙是為了妳…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.69,0:20:34.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你別說多餘的話
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.57,0:20:36.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了我？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.22,0:20:37.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.57,0:20:41.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了能讓妳所期待的學園祭成功舉辦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.79,0:20:44.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丹童子 你也一樣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.55,0:20:46.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.47,0:20:50.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們兩個人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.19,0:20:55.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向我發誓再也不會瞞著我跟惡石戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.41,0:20:57.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.73,0:20:59.07,SP1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.47,0:20:59.07,SP2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遵命　　　　
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.14,0:21:04.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我很感謝你們能保護了學院祭
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.07,0:21:06.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的很感謝你們
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.35,0:21:10.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說 不介意的話 這個…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.71,0:21:11.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請用
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.79,0:21:16.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喔 正好肚子餓了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.22,0:21:17.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可以全吃了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.95,0:21:21.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要留下我那份啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.53,0:21:28.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學院祭那天 天公作美
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.84,0:21:31.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,眾多來賓大駕光臨
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.71,0:21:33.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們礦石部也盛況空前
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.09,0:21:37.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在文化部的展覽中獲得了第二名
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.34,0:21:40.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然我推薦的「記錄 石頭的24小時」
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.92,0:21:43.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出人意料的沒什麼人氣 真是遺憾啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.21,0:21:45.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些孩子們明明都很可愛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.17,0:21:49.51,Notes,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鏡同學 再靠左邊點
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.12,0:21:49.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管怎麼說 學院祭無事終了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.57,0:21:51.57,Notes,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}表彰
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.57,0:21:51.57,Notes,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}COSPLAY特別獎 丹童子阿爾瑪殿下 鏡誠殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.57,0:21:51.57,Notes,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}你在第一屆藍羽學園祭COSPLAY部門中
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.57,0:21:51.57,Notes,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}就如正文所述 獲得了優異的成績
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.57,0:21:51.57,Notes,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}在此對你們進行表彰
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.57,0:21:51.57,Notes,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}藍羽學園 學園祭施行委員會
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.14,0:21:51.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了對了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.50,0:21:53.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實丹童子同學和鏡同學
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.65,0:21:55.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也因為前幾天的活躍而受到了好評
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.94,0:21:58.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得到了COSPLAY特別獎呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.19,0:22:07.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 要結束了呢 真是意猶未盡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.22,0:22:09.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.52,0:22:12.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近這飲料賣得很好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.25,0:22:13.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳知道的真清楚啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.04,0:22:15.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我家是開藥店的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.97,0:22:17.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個真的那麼好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.07,0:22:20.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個飲料啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.47,0:22:30.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您怎麼了 大小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.59,0:22:32.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼事都沒有！！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.61,0:22:34.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是您的臉色…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.55,0:22:35.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通紅啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.05,0:22:38.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連阿爾瑪同學也…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.47,0:22:40.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真丟臉

